Context: The Centre for Construction and Engineering Technologies at George Brown College accepts donations to support student scholarships. Donors will receive charitable tax receipts. Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and other information can be obtained by signing up on the website or contacting ask.george@georgebrown.ca.
